---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Add a City | CourtScope"><section class="section"><div class="shell"><p class="eyebrow">Expansion instructions</p><h1>Help CourtScope evaluate another city</h1><p>Submitting sources does not guarantee activation. A city can become active only after source, privacy, identity, court-separation, and statistical gates pass.</p><div class="grid grid-2"><article class="card"><h2>What to provide</h2><ul><li>Official source URLs or datasets</li><li>Data dictionaries and field maps</li><li>API or portal documentation</li><li>Election and judge identity files</li><li>Notes on court types and case identifiers</li></ul></article><article class="card"><h2>Supported formats</h2><p>CSV, JSON, XLSX, PDF, HTML, sample records, source maps, data dictionaries, official URLs, API documentation, scraper notes, and election files.</p></article></div><h2>Hard blocks</h2><ul><li>Unverifiable or unauthorized sources</li><li>Unresolved judge identity collisions</li><li>Unusable case identifiers</li><li>Missing required model variables</li><li>Inability to separate court types</li><li>Privacy, secret, migration, or scoring risk</li></ul><a class="button" href="/records">Submit source information</a></div></section></BaseLayout>
